@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="mt-5 container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>

    <hr />

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information when you use our website:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal information (e.g., name, email address, phone number).</li>
        <li>Account details (e.g., username, password).</li>
        <li>Usage data (e.g., pages visited, time spent on the site).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services.</li>
        <li>Personalize your experience on the site.</li>
        <li>Send notifications, updates, and promotional content (if opted-in).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Service providers who assist us in operating our website.</li>
        <li>Authorities if required by law or to protect our legal rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take appropriate measures to ensure your data is protected. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing (where applicable).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this page periodically for the latest information on our privacy practices.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@webcontrollibrary.com">support@webcontrollibrary.com</a></li>
        <li>Phone: +1 123-456-7890</li>
    </ul>
</div>
